Sau khi trao i, hai bn thng nht lp hp ng giao dch vi ni dung v nhng iu khon sau:
iu 1: NI DUNG HP NG

iu 2: NGHA V CA BN B
1) Trong vng ti a 2h k t thi im nhn hp ng, Bn B phi lin h vi ph huynh/hc vin.
2) Khi n gp ti bui u tin, Bn B phi gi cho ph huynh/hc vin giy gii thiu gia s. Trong
trng hp nhn lp online, Bn B phi in giy gii thiu gia s c nh km trong email.
3) Khi n gp ti bui u tin, Bn B phi xut trnh cho ph huynh/hc vin xem bn gc (hoc bn
sao, nh chp) cc loi giy t: Th sinh vin (nu l sinh vin), Th gio vin (nu l gio vin), Chng
minh th nhn dn (hoc th cn cc).
4) Bn B phi chun b gio trnh, gio n trc khi ging dy. ng thi m bo c lch hc v thi
gian ging dy cho ph huynh/hc vin. (Nu v l do bt kh khng, Bn B phi bo trc cho ph
huynh/hc vin t nht 2 gi).
5) Bn B phi thng bo cho Bn A trong thi gian ti a 24h, k t thi im pht sinh cc s c: khng
lin h c vi ph huynh/hc vin; ph huynh/hc vin khng sp xp c lch hc; ph huynh/hc
vin thng bo gim s bui hc/tun, gim hc ph, tm dng lp, hy lp; cc s c nghim trng khc.
6) Bn B lu s in thoi ca Bn A (0967-888-280) Bn A tin lin h nu lp xy ra s c. Trng
hp Bn B khng nghe in thoi, Bn B phi gi li cho bn A mun nht 4h k t khi c cuc gi nh.
7) Bn B khng c chuyn giao lp hc cho ngi khc.
iu 3: CHNH SCH HC TH CA HC SINH / HC VIN
1) Ni dung chnh sch:
Hc sinh/hc vin c quyn hc th vi gia s qua 2 bui hc u tin. Sau 2 bui ny:
- Nu khng ng nhn gia s, ph huynh/hc vin khng phi thanh ton hc ph;
- Nu ng v tip tc hc, ph huynh/hc vin s thanh ton hc ph ca c 2 bui ny cho gia s.
2) Bn B (gia s) phi c ngha v truyn t r rng chnh sch ny n ph huynh/hc vin. Chnh sch
ny c trong giy gii thiu gia s, Bn B phi a cho ph huynh/hc vin gi trong bui gp mt u
tin. Nu Bn B nhn lp online, Bn B phi t in giy gii thiu gia s (nh km trong email).
iu 4: PHT HP NG
Bn B s b pht 100% gi tr hp ng, nu xy ra 1 trong cc trng hp sau:
1) Bn B khng thc hin y ngha v ca mnh thuc iu 2 hoc iu 3;
2) Bn B tuyn b mnh khng th ging dy tt, khin lp b hy;
3) Bn B khng sp xp c lch dy, khin lp b hy hoc b gim s bui/tun;
4) Bn B c thi , cch c x khng ng chun mc, khin lp b hy;
5) Lp b hy hoc b gim s bui/tun do nhng l do c nhn xut pht t Bn B (Bn B vin c nh
xa, khng tin xe bus, di chuyn n a im khc, Bn B khai bo thng tin khng ng s tht, ...);
6) Bn B t b lp (k c cc trng hp lp b gim s bui hc/tun, lp gp s c) m khng c s
cho php ca Bn A.
Lu : Trong trng hp Bn B n ph, nu Bn B b pht hp ng, Bn B vn phi thanh ton y
v ng hn s ph nhn lp cho Bn A theo iu 6 ca hp ng.
iu 5: NGHA V CA BN A
Nu Bn B khng vi phm mt trong cc iu 2, iu 3, iu 4 ca hp ng, Bn A s m bo quyn
li ca Bn B khi lp gp s c. C th:
Bn A s xc minh thng tin vi ph huynh/hc vin v s c ca lp, nu thng tin l ng s tht,
ng thi Bn B khng c cc du hiu khai bo gian ln, Bn A s:
1) Tnh li ph nhn lp
a. Trng hp ph huynh/hc vin hy lp (s bui dy nh hn hoc bng 2): Ph nhn lp = 0 .
b. Trng hp ph huynh/hc vin kt thc lp hc sm (s bui dy nh hn s bui hc/tun 4):
Ph nhn lp = hc ph/bui tng s bui dy thc t mc % ph nhn lp ban u.
c. Cc trng hp lp b gim hc ph, gim s bui hc/tun (iu kin: thi gian gim s bui hc/tun
phi ko di t nht 4 tun lin tip), s da vo s liu thc t: Ph nhn lp = hc ph/bui s bui
hc/tun 4 mc % ph nhn lp ban u.
2) S tin cn d sau khi tnh li ph nhn lp, s c Bn A hon li cho Bn B.
iu 6: PH NHN LP
Tt c bao gm: ph qun l gia s, xc minh thng tin, lm hp ng, t vn ph huynh/hc vin, qun
l thng tin lp hc, x l cc s c pht sinh.
